 đạo pháp thần thông cải cách đại thế.</strong></p>","tmdb":{"type":"tv","id":"236534","season":1,"vote_average":8.25,"vote_count":12},"modified":"2026-03-31T10:23:42.000Z","cast":["Zhang Ruoyu","Yao Mingshun","Xin Li","Cheng Yuzhu","Du Qingqing","Xiao Xu YU","Gao Sihang","Tang Hao","Zhang Heng","Wang Yuhang","Liu Yuxuan"],"director":["沈乐平"],"cast_meta":[{"name":"Zhang Ruoyu","name_vi":null,"name_original":"Zhang Ruoyu","tmdb_id":3718807,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/xqmmuN34EtJ50xqqrvD3fB7QVX4.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/3718807"},{"name":"Yao Mingshun","name_vi":null,"name_original":"Yao Mingshun","tmdb_id":4783240,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/zODOUTvGaoeXH2ITUxmwNUPR9KI.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/4783240"},{"name":"Xin Li","name_vi":null,"name_original":"Xin Li","tmdb_id":4967724,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/6daNeAZ9Oys6S4YoXfcTSxq8tDj.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/4967724"},{"name":"Cheng Yuzhu","name_vi":null,"name_original":"Cheng Yuzhu","tmdb_id":3171082,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/1OoKCFRvTACC1O25qMqtditbCTb.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/3171082"},{"name":"Du Qingqing","name_vi":null,"name_original":"Du Qingqing","tmdb_id":2722648,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/l4sCRMlddNFCeywWoU99SbrxaEn.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/2722648"},{"name":"Xiao Xu YU","name_vi":null,"name_original":"Xiao Xu YU","tmdb_id":4751082,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/2DpDqUB2bnr8SUPGcOJgZ2Tn0Xt.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/4751082"},{"name":"Gao Sihang","name_vi":null,"name_original":"Gao Sihang","tmdb_id":4764177,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/8IIPqT9juefSHsO5F48rTysnv7p.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/4764177"},{"name":"Tang Hao","name_vi":null,"name_original":"Tang Hao","tmdb_id":3130715,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/l8wliv3AGoSF65